        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T06n0220_337:0728b03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等疾證無上正等菩提，利樂有情無邊際故。",
        "from": "T06n0220_337:0728b03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「苾芻當知！",
        "from": "T06n0220_337:0728b04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等功德智慧，亦勝菩薩摩訶薩遠離般若波羅蜜多方便善巧，嚴淨佛土、成熟有情者。",
        "from": "T06n0220_337:0728b05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T06n0220_337:0728b07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等疾證無上正等菩提，利樂有情無邊際故。",
